data.description: MAJOR PRICE $$$ REDUCTION…. SELLER MOTIVATED TO SELL…. BRING AN OFFER. Welcome to this stunning two-story single-family home nestled in the charming city of Apopka, Florida. Boasting 4 bedrooms and 2.5 baths, this residence offers an exquisite blend of modern luxury and comfortable living. As you step inside, you'll immediately be captivated by the thoughtful design and attention to detail. The inviting living room, complete with a cozy fireplace, creates an atmosphere of warmth and elegance, perfect for gatherings with family and friends on cool evenings. The heart of this home is the well-appointed kitchen, which features great appliances and granite countertops, ample counter space, and sleek cabinetry. Whether you're a culinary enthusiast or simply enjoy hosting meals, this kitchen provides the ideal backdrop for creating memorable dining experiences.  One of the standout features of this residence is the master bedroom, conveniently located on the main floor. This sanctuary of relaxation offers a peaceful retreat after a long day, and the en-suite bathroom with its luxurious finishes and spa-like amenities provides the ultimate indulgence.  Upstairs, you'll find three generously sized bedrooms that offer both comfort and privacy for family members or guests. The thoughtfully designed layout ensures everyone has their own space to unwind and recharge. Situated on a sprawling 0.63-acre lot, this property offers an outdoor oasis that is both expansive and private. The possibilities are endless, whether you envision lush gardens, a serene outdoor entertainment area. Located in the desirable city of Apopka, you'll enjoy easy access to local conveniences, schools, parks, and recreational activities. This home strikes the perfect balance between tranquility and accessibility, providing an enviable lifestyle for those seeking the best of both worlds. This 2-story single-family home in Apopka, FL presents an exceptional opportunity to own a residence that combines timeless design, modern comforts, and a spacious lot. Don't miss your chance to experience the epitome of gracious Florida living – schedule your private viewing today. Roof was replaced within the last 6 years, There are 2 A/C Units, one got replaced within the last 5-7 years, both have been serviced 2 weeks ago.
